 class CompareHandler.ByteBufferType
extends Object
implements org.eclipse.compare.ITypedElement, org.eclipse.compare.IStreamContentAccessor

Class used to implement needed ITypedElement interface which is needed for the compare editor. The class handles only the original update file extract from the data base.
